  "detailed_description": "“Infinity Blocks” is a jigsaw type puzzle game.<br><br>The goal in the game is to fill the gray areas of each level with blue blocks, and the order in which the blocks are placed is the key to puzzle.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2617110/extras/66f6f3035d84586f32f55b876fa67e43.poster.avif?t=1718430108\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2617110/extras/66f6f3035d84586f32f55b876fa67e43.webm?t=1718430108\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2617110/extras/66f6f3035d84586f32f55b876fa67e43.mp4?t=1718430108\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The blocks in the game have a variety of special effects, such as rotating or moving other blocks when they are placed.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2617110/extras/6e1e4c4ebace10f6675b274a998fb250.webp?t=1718430108\" width=32 height=32 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2617110/extras/790d43ec61a5884c267c0e7bf037fdc2.webp?t=1718430108\" width=32 height=32 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2617110/extras/9d0661ffa90a415418fb82e6f2e6ff93.webp?t=1718430108\" width=32 height=32 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2617110/extras/b75d3fc9d2138cb3566efef60e9048a4.webp?t=1718430108\" width=32 height=32 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2617110/extras/bfbc420ba8